          everything going on as they happen!
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-family="Hind" line-height="150%" font-size="14px" color="#4D4D4D">
          We'll also have a live site with the schedule, announcements, and
          everything else you need to know at
          <a href="https://mchacks.ca" style="color: #F2463A; text-decoration: none;">mchacks.ca</a>
          closer to the event
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-include path="./HackingPolicy.mjml" />
    <mj-include path="./SocialMedia.mjml" />
